Date: Fri 3 Mar 2006
From: "Dr Alfonso J Rodriguez" <ajrm_msds@yahoo.es>
Source: Mipunto.com, Agence France Presse (AFP) report, Thu 2 Mar 2006
(translated from Spanish by AJR) [edited]
